SUMMER 2023 FINDINGS
From June 1, 2022 through August 5, 2022, nine SMU Law student volunteers observed 1,135 cases: 464 in Justice of the Peace Court 1-1, 344 in Justice of the Peace Court 3-1, and 327 in Justice of the Peace Court 5-1. The 1,135 observed cases represent 32% coverage of all initially scheduled hearings in 1-1, 3-1, and 5-1.










