*The reason for an eviction case might be unknown if a default judgment was awarded to a landlord and the facts of the case were not discussed. Reasons are rounded to the nearest whole number, so totals may not equal 100%.
 Why this matters: In Dallas County, millions of dollars for rent relief have been available throughout the pandemic. Eviction cases due to nonpayment of rent might have been remedied had the renter and landlord been aware of and able to easily access rent relief programs.
